tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ML_Algorithms (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  algorithm_name VARCHAR(100),
  model_type VARCHAR(100),
  accuracy DECIMAL(5,2),
  training_time INTERVAL,
  hyperparameters JSON
);
CREATE TABLE data_patterns (id INT, column_1 VARCHAR(255), column_2 VARCHAR(255), column_3 INT);
CREATE TABLE data_distributions (id INT, feature_1 VARCHAR(255), feature_2 VARCHAR(255), label INT);
CREATE TABLE machine_learning_insights (id INT, model_name VARCHAR(255), accuracy FLOAT, precision FLOAT, recall FLOAT);
CREATE TABLE data_analysis_queries (id INT, query_name VARCHAR(255), query_text TEXT);
